---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Nav from '../components/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Terms of Service — eKosha"
  description="Read the terms and conditions governing your use of eKosha."
>
  <Nav />
  <main class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-24">
    <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-2">Terms of Service</h1>
    <p class="text-brand-muted mb-10 text-sm">Last updated: April 12, 2026 &nbsp;·&nbsp; Effective date: April 12, 2026</p>

    <section class="mb-10">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-brand-navy mb-3">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
      <p class="text-brand-text leading-relaxed">
        By creating an account and using eKosha, you agree to these Terms of Service ("Terms"). If you do not agree, do not use the app.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-10">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-brand-navy mb-3">2. Description of Service</h2>
      <p class="text-brand-text leading-relaxed">
        eKosha provides a secure digital vault for personal financial asset management, inheritance planning, and controlled sharing with trusted individuals.
        The service is operated by <strong>eKosha</strong>.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-10">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-brand-navy mb-3">3. Eligibility</h2>
      <p class="text-brand-text leading-relaxed">
        You must be at least <strong>18 years old</strong> to use eKosha. By using the service, you represent that you meet this requirement.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-10">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-brand-navy mb-3">4. Your Account</h2>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-brand-text">
        <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-brand-gold font-bold shrink-0">·</span><span>You are responsible for maintaining the confidentiality of your account credentials.</span></li>
        <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-brand-gold font-bold shrink-0">·</span><span>You are responsible for all activities under your account.</span></li>
        <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-brand-gold font-bold shrink-0">·</span><span>Notify us immediately if you suspect unauthorised access.</span></li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-10">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-brand-navy mb-3">5. Acceptable Use</h2>
      <p class="text-brand-text leading-relaxed mb-3">You agree not to:</p>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-brand-text">
        <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-brand-gold font-bold shrink-0">·</span><span>Provide false or misleading information.</span></li>
        <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-brand-gold font-bold shrink-0">·</span><span>Use the service for any unlawful purpose.</span></li>
        <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-brand-gold font-bold shrink-0">·</span><span>Attempt to gain unauthorised access to other users' data.</span></li>
        <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-brand-gold font-bold shrink-0">·</span><span>Reverse engineer, decompile, or disassemble the application.</span></li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-10">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-brand-navy mb-3">6. Data and Privacy</h2>
      <p class="text-brand-text leading-relaxed">
        Your use of the service is subject to our <a href="/privacy" class="text-brand-gold underline">Privacy Policy</a>, which is incorporated into these Terms by reference.
        You retain ownership of all data you upload to eKosha.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-10">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-brand-navy mb-3">7. Subscriptions</h2>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-brand-text">
        <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-brand-gold font-bold shrink-0">·</span><span>The Free plan includes limited asset and sharing slots.</span></li>
        <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-brand-gold font-bold shrink-0">·</span><span>The Premium plan is available on a monthly (₹99/month) or annual (₹899/year) basis, with a 7-day free trial.</span></li>
        <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-brand-gold font-bold shrink-0">·</span><span>Payments are processed through the Apple App Store or Google Play Store.</span></li>
        <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-brand-gold font-bold shrink-0">·</span><span>Refunds are subject to the respective platform's refund policy.</span></li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-10">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-brand-navy mb-3">8. Limitation of Liability</h2>
      <p class="text-brand-text leading-relaxed">
        To the maximum extent permitted by applicable law, eKosha shall not be liable for any indirect, incidental, special, or consequential damages.
        Our total liability for any claim arising from the service shall not exceed the amount you paid us in the 12 months preceding the claim.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-10">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-brand-navy mb-3">9. Indemnification</h2>
      <p class="text-brand-text leading-relaxed">
        You agree to indemnify and hold harmless eKosha and its officers from any claims, losses, or damages arising from your violation of these Terms or applicable law.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-10">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-brand-navy mb-3">10. Termination</h2>
      <p class="text-brand-text leading-relaxed">
        We may suspend or terminate your account if you breach these Terms. You may delete your account at any time from
        <strong>Settings &gt; Privacy &amp; Data &gt; Delete Account</strong>.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-10">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-brand-navy mb-3">11. Governing Law and Dispute Resolution</h2>
      <p class="text-brand-text leading-relaxed">
        These Terms are governed by the laws of <strong>India</strong>. Any dispute shall be subject to the exclusive jurisdiction of the courts of <strong>Maharashtra, India</strong>.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-10">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-brand-navy mb-3">12. Changes to Terms</h2>
      <p class="text-brand-text leading-relaxed">
        We will notify you of material changes. Continued use after notification constitutes acceptance.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-10">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-brand-navy mb-3">13. Contact</h2>
      <p class="text-brand-text leading-relaxed">
        For questions about these Terms, email us at{' '}
        <a href="mailto:privacy@ekosha.co.in" class="text-brand-gold underline">privacy@ekosha.co.in</a>.
      </p>
    </section>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
